Sami Frey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sami_Frey 0 Sami Frey (born Samuel Frei on 13 October 1937) is a French actor of Polish Jewish descent. Among the films he starred in are En compagnie d'Antonin Artaud (1993), in which he portrays French poet and playwright Antonin Artaud, and Bande à part (1964) by Jean-Luc Godard.
